text:
Once a fox was out  
searching for food.  
He was very hungry.

He came upon a vineyard full of grapes.   
They looked very tasty.   
His mouth watered.  
He jumped up to the nearest   
bunch of grapes that was hanging down.  He could 
not reach them.

He tried and tried, and soon got tired  but could not 
reach the grapes. Sadly,  he walked away saying to 
himself,  Anyway, the grapes were sour.
